{"tid":1692212,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"英國脫歐 點解一拖再拖？學術討論","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T05:20:43.000Z","uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40758e267b304f43a6656c2f4f978608455ee5bb","tid":1692212,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:33:33.000Z","msg":"拋磚先，整左條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ENIkL21JqtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FENIkL21JqtQ&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWftOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=c46b27bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ENIkL21JqtQ</a><br />\n<br />\n拖黎拖去，根本個個都唔知點做，冇人知點收科！硬脫歐又驚比國民屌到反艇；協議又傾唔到，歐盟唔9理你，真係殘局，同香港呢個局一樣唔知點解開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2143e7d78a5e939fd32883afd4f5e225adff708c","tid":1692212,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:17:35.000Z","msg":"歐盟並唔係一個會籍咁簡單嘅是非題<br />\n而係一系列互相牽連嘅國際條約組成<br />\n（好似唔加入歐元區咁，其他民生方面嘅融合問題可以拎出嚟單獨傾架嘛）<br />\n尤其是英國呢個本身都係 Kingdom of kingdoms<br />\n(我都唔明點解有人話英國係單一制國家，明明蘇格蘭北愛個地位都唔同英格蘭威爾斯)<br />\n其實本身就唔係好適合用公投二分法嚟做決定<br />\n底下嘅細節太多<br />\n甚至乎北愛 hard border 問題原來喺公投前無詳細傾過無 way out<br />\n公投變咗純粹嘅意氣之爭感情宣泄<br />\n實務問題無充足討論<br />\n制度上究竟係國會最大定公投最大<br />\n而家都未有清楚結論<br />\n（如果話國會最大，PM 其實無 mandate 無動機堅持脫歐，直接宣佈唔會脫歐好嘛）"},{"pid":"c57acc840f86ecaf249d750800c46a2622909432","tid":1692212,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"Hard brexit<br />\n之後再同eu 簽free trade agreement"},{"pid":"7f5c2e8794d738e323402ab4a13bccfa2f0a6020","tid":1692212,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c57acc840f86ecaf249d750800c46a2622909432","tid":1692212,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"Hard brexit<br />\n之後再同eu 簽free trade agreement"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"佢都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}